### =============================================================================
### dhan-live-trader — QuestDB SQL Queries
### =============================================================================
### Run any query: click the green play button next to it.
### QuestDB must be running (Docker Up) before testing.
### Environment: select "dev" from the dropdown (top-right) before running.
### Uses QuestDB REST API on port 9000.
### =============================================================================

### ---- Schema Discovery ----

### Show all tables
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SHOW%20TABLES

###

### Show columns of ticks table
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SHOW%20COLUMNS%20FROM%20ticks

###

### Show columns of derivative_contracts table
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SHOW%20COLUMNS%20FROM%20derivative_contracts

###

### ---- Tick Queries ----

### Latest 10 ticks (most recent first)
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20*%20FROM%20ticks%20ORDER%20BY%20ts%20DESC%20LIMIT%2010

###

### Tick count per day
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20ts%3A%3Adate%20AS%20day%2C%20count()%20FROM%20ticks%20SAMPLE%20BY%201d

###

### ---- Instrument Queries ----

### Latest F&O underlyings
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20*%20FROM%20fno_underlyings%20ORDER%20BY%20timestamp%20DESC%20LIMIT%2020

###

### Derivative contracts count per snapshot
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20timestamp%3A%3Adate%20AS%20day%2C%20count(DISTINCT%20security_id)%20AS%20contract_count%20FROM%20derivative_contracts%20SAMPLE%20BY%201d

###

### ---- System Queries ----

### QuestDB server version
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20version()

###

### Table sizes (row counts)
GET {{questdb_host}}/exec?query=SELECT%20table_name%2C%20partitionBy%2C%20designatedTimestamp%20FROM%20tables()
